### Set environment variables
@host = http://localhost:8080/api/payments
@wompiHost = http://localhost:8080/api/payments/wompi
@authToken = Bearer tu_token_aqui
@paymentId = id_de_tu_pago_aqui
@orderId = id_de_tu_orden_aqui
@customerId = 1

### ============================================
### 1. CREAR PAGO (MÉTODOS TRADICIONALES)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Crear pago en efectivo
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "amount": 25000.0,
  "paymentMethod": "EFECTIVO",
  "notes": "Pago en efectivo del pedido"
}

### 1.2 Crear pago con tarjeta física (sin Stripe)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "amount": 35000.0,
  "paymentMethod": "TARJETA_FISICA",
  "transactionId": "TXN123456789",
  "notes": "Pago con tarjeta física"
}

### ============================================
### 2. CONSULTAR PAGOS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Obtener todos los pagos
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 2.2 Obtener detalle de un pago específico
GET {{host}}/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### 3. PAGOS CON WOMPI (PASARELA COLOMBIANA)
### ============================================
### ⚠️ IMPORTANTE: Para usar Wompi necesitas:
### 1. Obtener token de Wompi desde el cliente (Wompi.js)
### 2. Reemplazar "reference_token" con tu token real de Wompi
### 3. Usar el ORDEN_ID y CLIENTE_ID reales
### 4. Los montos están en CENTAVOS COP
### 5. Wompi solo funciona con COP (pesos colombianos)

### 3.1 Confirmar pago con Wompi (Monto 50,000 COP = $500 COP)
### Este endpoint procesa un pago con tarjeta de crédito via Wompi
POST {{wompiHost}}/confirm
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "wompiToken": "eJydUsFuwjAM_RWLT",
  "amount": 5000000,
  "description": "Pago de orden de comida en Smart Restaurant",
  "customerEmail": "cliente@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "+573001234567",
  "notes": "Cliente premium - descuento aplicado"
}

### 3.2 Confirmar pago con Wompi (Monto menor - 25,000 COP = $250 COP)
POST {{wompiHost}}/confirm
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "wompiToken": "eJydUsFuwjAM_ZWLT",
  "amount": 2500000,
  "description": "Pago parcial de orden",
  "customerEmail": "cliente@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "+573001234567",
  "notes": "Pago a plazos"
}

### 3.3 Confirmar pago con Wompi (Monto pequeño - 100 COP)
### Monto mínimo típico en Wompi
POST {{wompiHost}}/confirm
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "wompiToken": "eJydUsFuwjAM_ZWLT",
  "amount": 10000,
  "description": "Bebida pequeña",
  "customerEmail": "cliente@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "+573001234567",
  "notes": "Adicional a la orden principal"
}

### ============================================
### 5. REEMBOLSOS
### ============================================

### 5.1 Reembolsar un pago de Stripe
POST {{host}}/{{paymentId}}/refund
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5.2 Reembolsar un pago de Wompi
POST {{host}}/{{paymentId}}/wompi/refund
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### TOKENS DE STRIPE PARA PRUEBAS
### ============================================
###
### ✅ Pagos exitosos:
### - tok_visa: Tarjeta Visa válida
### - tok_mastercard: Tarjeta Mastercard válida
### - tok_amex: Tarjeta American Express válida
###
### ❌ Pagos fallidos:
### - tok_chargeDeclined: Declinado
### - tok_chargeDeclinedFraudulent: Fraude
### - tok_raiseAlert: Alerta
###
### NOTA: Estos tokens solo funcionan en TEST MODE
### En producción usarás tokens reales de Stripe.js
###
### ============================================
### INFORMACIÓN SOBRE WOMPI
### ============================================
###
### 🇨🇴 Wompi es la pasarela de pagos para Colombia
###
### Endpoints:
### - Test: https://staging.wompi.co/api
### - Producción: https://production.wompi.co/api
###
### Tokens de prueba (Test Mode):
### - eJydUsFuwjAM_ZWLT: Token de prueba válido
### - eJydUsFuwjAM_WJLT: Otro token de prueba
###
### Moneda: COP (pesos colombianos)
### - Los montos se envían en CENTAVOS
### - 100 = $1.00 COP
### - 5,000,000 = $50,000 COP
###
### Información requerida:
### - Token de Wompi (generado en cliente con Wompi.js)
### - Email del cliente
### - Teléfono del cliente (formato: +57XXXXXXXXXX)
### - Descripción del pago
### - ID único de referencia (orderId)
###
### Respuesta exitosa (status):
### - APPROVED: Pago aprobado
### - PENDING: Pago pendiente
### - DECLINED: Pago rechazado
###
### ============================================

